╝┴ŪĀ£ ▀Æ█	(?0å▌~8U@	ĆSCAN([IS T1]) | FLATMAP q0 -> { SCAN([IS T3]) | FLATMAP q1 -> { SCAN([IS T2]) | FILTER q1.T2_ID EQUALS _.ID AND _.T1_ID EQUALS q0.ID AS q2 RETURN (@c8 AS _0) } | DEFAULT NULL | FLATMAP q3 -> { SCAN([IS T2]) | FILTER _.T1_ID EQUALS q0.ID | MAP (@c8 AS _0) | DEFAULT NULL AS q4 RETURN (q4 AS _0, q3 AS _1) } AS q5 RETURN (q0.ID AS ID, exists(q5._0) AS HAS_T2, exists(q5._1) AS HAS_T3) }┌?digraph G {
  fontname=courier;
  rankdir=BT;
